7e57b831-9f45-4160-9353-d8566a567977.title: Delta Force 1
7e57b831-9f45-4160-9353-d8566a567977.summary: Delta Force is a tactical first-person shooter developed and published by NovaLogic. It was released for the Windows in October 1998. Delta Force was designed to be a military simulation loosely based on the United States' Delta Force special operations army unit.

099d2ded-4790-4288-b0ae-0ba366bf6e88.title: Counter Strike 1.6
099d2ded-4790-4288-b0ae-0ba366bf6e88.summary: Counter-Strike (also known as Half-Life: Counter-Strike or Counter-Strike 1.6) is a 2000 tactical first-person shooter game developed by Valve Corporation and published by Sierra Studios. It is the first installment in the Counter-Strike series.
